title.rendered: Luxurious 4BHK Apartment For Sale In GK-2

content.rendered:
You’re bound to be impressed by this magnificent 460yds builder floor which is nestled in the most upscale location of #southdelhi. This beautiful apartment is set on a sprawling 460yds and has a very tasteful drawing/dining room, tidy bedrooms with connected luxury baths and balconies, a fully loaded Italian modular kitchen, an exclusive driveway and lift, and 2 car stilt parking.

♕GK-2
♕460yds
♕4BHK
♕Italian Modular Kitchen
♕Tasteful Drawing/Dining
♕Luxurious Builder Floor
♕Wide Road
♕Exclusive Driveway
♕Newly Constructed Apartment
♕100% Power Backup-Up
♕A+ Construction
♕Ready To Move In
♕Elite Location

Lalit Kaushik

Call On 98183-12077 For More Information

http://wa.me/919818312077

Follow @royalerealtorsindia on social media

Checkout Our Other Listings Here

ROYALE REALTORS INDIA

19 DDA Market, Shanti Niketan, New Delhi, Delhi 110021
